29
00:01:37,427 --> 00:01:40,366
A: Well, would you mind
my reforming myself this afternoon?

30
00:01:40,390 --> 00:01:42,339
C: Oh, that's rather quixotic of you,

31
00:01:42,363 --> 00:01:43,815
but I think you should try.

32
00:01:43,839 --> 00:01:46,064
A: Good. I feel better already.

33
00:01:46,088 --> 00:01:47,737
C: You're looking a little worse.

34
00:01:47,761 --> 00:01:51,403
A: Well, might I have that pink rose?

35
00:01:51,427 --> 00:01:52,578
C: Why?

36
00:01:52,602 --> 00:01:55,197
A: Because you are
like a pink rose, cousin Cecily.

37
00:01:55,221 --> 00:01:57,502
C: Well, I don't think
