39
00:01:58,718 --> 00:02:01,351
A: You are the prettiest girl I ever saw.

40
00:02:01,375 --> 00:02:04,581
C: But -- well, I -- I --

41
00:02:04,605 --> 00:02:06,513
A: And, and ahem --

42
