C: All good looks are a snare and --

43
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:12,238
A: Well, it's a snare
that every sensible man

44
00:02:12,262 --> 00:02:14,283
would like to be caught in, and ...

45
00:02:14,982 --> 00:02:16,402
Jo Michael Rezes: (Sighs)

46
